      <title>中国自六月以来首次下调抵押贷款参考利率</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-seen-cutting-mortgage-reference-rate-first-time-since-june-2024-02-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们普遍预计，中国将于周二将基准抵押贷款参考利率下调至月度固定利率，因为银行净息差的改善使当局有一定的余地，可以利用货币刺激措施来支撑步履蹒跚的经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-seen-cutting-mortgage-reference-rate-first-time-since-june-2024-02-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 07:15:26 GMT</pubDate>
